.TH VITTE-EDITOR 1 "March 2026" "vitte 2.1.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
vitte-editor \- graphical multi-file editor for Vitte projects
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B vitte-editor
[\fIproject-or-file\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B vitte-editor
launches the VitteEditor desktop application.
It provides multi-file tabs, syntax highlighting, completion suggestions,
and diagnostics via
.B vitte check --diag-json
.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
vitte-editor
vitte-editor /path/to/project
vitte-editor src/main.vit
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR vitte (1),
.BR vittec (1),
.BR vitte-linker (1)
